{"tid":1844018,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】醫管局：無意否定有醫護要抽「生死籤」","createTime":"2020-01-26T12:30:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T15:51:54.000Z","uid":226548,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"84a25dce2d8f34ec022a1da64839b04b7b8e6d18","tid":1844018,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T12:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200126/s00001/cd5a9083b40c6c45a378119fd2f35daf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200126%2Fs00001%2Fcd5a9083b40c6c45a378119fd2f35daf.jpg&h=3c3fd922&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情持續，本港有公院醫護人員抽「生死籤」照顧懷疑和確診患者。醫管局質素及安全總監鍾健禮昨（25日）稱當局着重醫護人員意願，「抽籤」用語於人事部政策無出現。他今午（26日）在記者會表示，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>無意否定醫護人員需抽籤</strong></span>，亦無意給予道德壓力，「如果我有令同事誤會地方，我講聲唔好意思」，並<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">承認若有需要，個別部門會抽籤</span></strong></span>。"},{"pid":"e0c95c64095685275b8f06d5dc1363b323f68959","tid":1844018,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T12:30:31.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200126/s00001/1580033957592/【武漢肺炎】鍾健禮-無意否定有醫護要抽「生死籤」\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200126%2Fs00001%2F1580033957592%2F%E3%80%90%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E9%8D%BE%E5%81%A5%E7%A6%AE-%E7%84%A1%E6%84%8F%E5%90%A6%E5%AE%9A%E6%9C%89%E9%86%AB%E8%AD%B7%E8%A6%81%E6%8A%BD%E3%80%8C%E7%94%9F%E6%AD%BB%E7%B1%A4%E3%80%8D&d=0fPPgjUU32Qc%2B%2Bj2t4ropFCKRJWvDXkpEFRbHtszOvM%3D&h=4e9e096e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200126%2Fs00001%2F1580033957592%2F%E3%80%90%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E9%8D%BE%E5%81%A5%E7%A6%AE-%E7%84%A1%E6%84%8F%E5%90%A6%E5%AE%9A%E6%9C%89%E9%86%AB%E8%AD%B7%E8%A6%81%E6%8A%BD%E3%